Encounter.Name: Ep1 - Phase 2: Payback Time
Encounter.Notes: In this phase, the PCs come across four artillery emplacements that they can man and attack two Imperial AT-STs that are nearby. You can print out the stock vehicle for the Arda I Anti-Vehicle Laser Cannon, of which there are two. The the Arda I Anti-Infantry Laser Cannons (also a stock vehicle) can be better utilitized in Phase 4.
